    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-102">Use o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.AudienceUriMode> propriedade em um aplicativo federado que utiliza um serviço de token de segurança (STS) que emite <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken> tokens de segurança.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-102">Use the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.AudienceUriMode> property in a federated application that utilizes a security token service (STS) that issues <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken> security tokens.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-103">Quando o STS emite o token de segurança, ele pode especificar o URI dos serviços da Web para o qual o token de segurança destina-se com a adição de um <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition> para o token de segurança.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-103">When the STS issues the security token, it can specify the URI of the Web services for which the security token is intended by adding a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition> to the security token.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-104">Que permite que o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator> para o serviço Web destinatário verificar se o token de segurança emitido destina-se para esse serviço da Web, especificando que essa seleção deve acontecer, fazendo o seguinte:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-104">That allows the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator> for the recipient Web service to verify that the issued security token is intended for this Web service by specifying that this check should happen by doing the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-105">Definir o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AudienceUriMode%2A> propriedade sempre ou BearerKeyOnly.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-105">Set the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AudienceUriMode%2A> property to Always or BearerKeyOnly.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-106">Especifique o conjunto de URIs válidos, adicionando os URIs para o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AllowedAudienceUris%2A> coleção.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-106">Specify the set of valid URIs, by adding the URIs to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AllowedAudienceUris%2A> collection.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dc5cd-107">Opcionalmente, substituir o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.ValidateAudienceRestriction%2A> método para especificar o algoritmo de validação a ser usado para o URI permitido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dc5cd-107">Optionally, override the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.ValidateAudienceRestriction%2A> method to specify the validation algorithm to use for the allowed URI.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
